  "_readme": "Source registry for qscrape. Entries hold EXTRACTION INSTRUCTIONS, never values, EXCEPT 'const' rules which are facts verified by hand against the named 'source' (used when the value lives in a JS-rendered page or PDF the stdlib fetcher cannot read). Every const carries an explicit source URL + method. Order of api_sources then spec_sources sets merge priority. Retrieval date is stamped at run time. Values verified 2026-07-06.",
