    "ibm": {
      "enabled": true,
      "emit_skips": true,
      "backends": [],
      "_note": "Set IBM_QUANTUM_TOKEN (or api_sources.ibm.token) + `pip install qiskit-ibm-runtime` for LIVE per-gate calibration: qubits, coupling-map edges, 1Q/2Q/SPAM fidelity stats, 1Q/2Q gate times, readout time, processor model, and Quantum Volume. Runs first, so its live values supersede the cited-const IBM entry and the CSV rows on merge. Optional 'backends' list restricts which devices are pulled (empty = all operational)."
